# Introduction

This project is a backend server that handles online marketplace functionalities

## Before Starting

- Fill the .env file

## To run the main server

- pip install -r requirements.txt
- python3 main.py

## DB Acces

- You can go to the env file and change the MONGODB_URI and connect to you local db and test the solution

## To run the stripe webhook server

- install stripe
  - install the stripe.deb from Github
  - sudo dpkg -i stripe.deb
  - to check if the installtion worked: stripe version
- stripe listen --forward-to localhost:8000/webhook

## To see all the APIs with interaction

- access: http://localhost:8000/docs
  - Here you can register and login
  - After logging in, take the token and authorize the APIs

## To run pytest

- python3 -m pytest src/tests/test_hash.py
